summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller and Ex-officio City Clerk, in the name of and in behalf of the City of Seattle, to make, execute and deliver unto the Seattle School District No. 1, a deed to Lots One (1), two (2), three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7), eight (8), twenty-five (25), twenty-six (26), twenty-seven (27), twenty-eight (28), twenty-nine (29), thirty (30), thirty-one (31) and thirty-two (32), Block Two (2) Parker's Addition to the City of Seattle, upon receipt of a good and sufficient deed from the Seattle School District No. 1 to Lots One (1), two (2), three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7), eight (8), twenty-five, twenty-six (26), twenty-seven (27), twenty-eight (28), twenty-nine (29), thirty (30), thirty-one (31) and thirty-two (32) in Block Three (3) Parker's Addition to the City of Seattle, in consideration, therefor.
